name: *NEW*dollie sleeping bag-brown floral
description:
Now you can bring your doll along on sleepovers with this cute sleeping bag and pillow!

This adorable sleeping bag is made out of soft comfy fleece. The pillow is detached and is made out of the same brown floral fabric. A pink grosgrain ribbon is attached at the bottom to roll up the bag and pillow together.

Sleeping Bag measures: 21" long
Pillow measures: 6"x8"

This sleeping bag is made to fit the American Girl 18 inch doll and other similar 18 inch dolls.

***Please note: this same sleeping bag can be made to fit a bitty baby doll as well.

Shipping is: $4.50 USPS fist class for the United State Only. Please contact me for international shipping cost.

Don't see exactly what you are looking for? I also do custom orders! Please contact me for more information.

name: messy flower hair clip-navy dots
description:
This adorable hair clip is made with gathered layers of fabric, sewn together to create a one-of-a kind messy flower clip and is topped off with a chubby covered button. This is the perfect clip for a cute little sweetie in your life. The fabric will fray over time, for a shabby chic look.

Your hair clip will come attached to our signature two little tots card, making your item ready to give as a gift.

Features:
•Attached to a 1.5” snap hair clip
•Messy flowers measure approx. 2-3”

Disclaimer:
Infants and children should be supervised while wearing hair accessories. Please be aware of choking hazards associated with any small parts.

Shipping is: $2.50 USPS fist class for the United State. Please contact me for international shipping cost.
